text: Tapa'ile bhannus ki timra sajhedaraharumadhye yasto ko cha? Jasale pahilo pataka pani srstiko prarambha garos ra tyasala'i dosro pataka pani dohoraya'os. Tapa'ile bhanidinus ki tyo allaha nai ho jasale srstiko suru'ata gardacha ra tyasako punaravrti pani gardacha, tasartha timi kaham pathabhramita bha'irakheka chau
